        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You fight hardest when the odds are at their most dire, and the specter of death looms over you. As long as you have temporary Hit Points from @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Heroic Last Stand]{Heroic Last Stand}, your Strikes and spells deal additional damage. You gain a status bonus to damage with your Strikes equal to the number of weapon damage dice. Spells you cast from spell slots gain a status bonus to damage equal to the level of the spell; this bonus applies only to spells that deal damage and don't have a duration.</p>"
